OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776809469
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports journalist Anna
OL,8,FYoussef with a special report
OL,10,FA mother who locked herself in her
OL,11,Fbedroom to protect herself from her
OL,12,Fson says it took him nearly dying
OL,13,Fbefore her family finally got the
OL,14,Fsupport they desperately needed.
OL,16,F"Sarah," who asked to remain
OL,17,Fanonymous, spent years begging for
OL,18,Fhelp as her son struggled with
OL,19,Fundiagnosed autism and ADHD, leading
OL,20,Fto frequent violent outbursts.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776809469
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FShe said: "He didn't have any respect
OL,8,Ffor me. He'd kick off, he'd smash the
OL,9,Fdoors up and smash the walls up - he'd
OL,10,Ftry going for me. I was scared every
OL,11,Fnight. I locked myself in my room.
OL,13,F"He just ruled the house and it was
OL,14,Flike walking on eggshells. I just felt
OL,15,Fas a parent this was all my fault,
OL,16,Flike I'm doing something wrong here."
OL,18,FWhen no help came, Sarah began to
OL,19,Fblame herself for her son's behaviour.
OL,26,@oD@KOUuD@AOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776809469
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FShe said: "I was crying out for help
OL,8,Fto social care about the child and
OL,9,Fparent abuse and even said if this was
OL,10,Fa boyfriend doing this to me, you'd be
OL,11,Ftelling me to leave or my child would
OL,12,Fbe taken away.
OL,14,F"I didn't feel like I was being the
OL,15,Fparent I should be. I felt like he'd
OL,16,Fbe better off without me. There were
OL,17,Ftimes I did get to the point of
OL,18,Foverdosing because I didn't know what
OL,19,Fto do anymore."
OL,26,@oD@KOUvD@AOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776809469
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FHer son was expelled from school at
OL,8,Fage 11 and became involved with gangs
OL,9,Fand criminality.
OL,11,FIt was only after he was stabbed and
OL,12,Fnearly died that Sarah finally got the
OL,13,Fhelp she had needed for so long.
OL,15,FWhile her son was in hospital, Sarah
OL,16,Fwas told about Encounter, a
OL,17,Ftherapeutic programme for parents
OL,18,Fstruggling with their child's
OL,19,Fbehaviour or neurodiversity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776809469
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThe support and skills she gained
OL,8,Fhelped make life easier at home, but
OL,9,FSarah says it almost came too late.
OL,11,FShe said: "It shouldn't take my child
OL,12,Fnearly being killed to get the correct
OL,13,Fkind of support`and this is coming
OL,14,Ffrom a charity, not our local
OL,15,Fauthority. I do think the system is
OL,16,Fbroken. I don't think it's there to
OL,17,Fsupport children with neurodiversity."
OL,26,@sD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
