FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776809469
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FReferrals to the Encounter programme
OL,8,Fare now at an all-time high, with many
OL,9,Fparents like Sarah facing similar
OL,10,Fabuse and in urgent need of help.
OL,12,FAnother mother, Leanne, now works for
OL,13,Fthe charity after her ten-year-old
OL,14,Fdaughter's abuse became so bad she
OL,15,Fregularly had to call the police.
OL,17,FShe said: "I felt like that was the
OL,18,Fonly help I could get at that time.
OL,19,FIt's horrible to say that you're
OL,20,Fterrified of a child."
OL,26,@yD@KOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776809469
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FLeanne described how her daughter took
OL,8,Fcontrol of the house.
OL,10,FShe said "She controlled everything. I
OL,11,Fwasn't allowed to speak on the phone
OL,12,Fwith anybody. I lived in my bedroom
OL,13,Ffor a whole year. She'd pull my hair.
OL,14,FShe'd punch me."
OL,16,FLeanne says the charity gave her
OL,17,Ffamily hope again, but two years on
OL,18,Fher daughter is still waiting for an
OL,19,Fautism and ADHD assessment.
OL,26,@rD@JOUvD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
