FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776809469
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FShe believes more needs to be done by
OL,8,Forganisations and authorities to
OL,9,Fsupport neurodivergent children and
OL,10,Ftheir families.
OL,12,FShe said: "Schools need more
OL,13,Funderstanding. More education on
OL,14,Fneurodiversity. I get that they have
OL,15,F(Special Educational Needs
OL,16,FCoordinators (SENCOs)) but there's
OL,17,Fonly so much one SENCO can do in a
OL,18,Fschool with 50 students that are
OL,19,Fneurodivergent."
OL,26,@wD@ApmxD@Vpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
