PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776809469
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FNicola Hill, team leader for Parent
OL,8,Fand Carer Support at Oasis, the
OL,9,Fcharity which runs the course, says
OL,10,Fearly intervention is key to better
OL,11,Flong-term outcomes and can reduce
OL,12,Fpressure on emergency services.
OL,14,FShe said: "You have to work with the
OL,15,Findividual and some people might think
OL,16,Fthat's like labour intensive or we
OL,17,Fcan't spend that much time but our
OL,18,Ffamilies are ringing the police.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776809469
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"They're ringing our services and
OL,8,Fputting in a great demand on emergency
OL,9,Fservices so we would eliminate that if
OL,10,Fwe are able to give these families the
OL,11,Fcorrect family support."
OL,13,FAs referrals to Encounter reach record
OL,14,Flevels, both mothers hope their
OL,15,Fstories will highlight the urgent need
OL,16,Ffor better early intervention and
OL,17,Fsupport for families in crisis.
OL,26,@sD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
